0Z","msg":"雖然思想唔係幾夾 又冇共同興趣<br />\n以前成日嫌佢悶 <br />\n但慢慢會發覺到佢好多細心既地方<br />\n只係我一路都唔為意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇左佢應該再搵唔返一個咁就得我既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15a9d21785e77ab323417136d8bb540331fc455","tid":2122172,"uid":202898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T10:40:22.000Z","msg":"對我大方<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0a6b1cc2f480e198399622bf0f5dabb58a104e","tid":2122172,"uid":301627,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T19:47:35.000Z","msg":"多謝男朋友欣賞我嘅幽默感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾包容我又肯就我，我成日要食好多嘢但你就算飽到死都陪我周圍食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就嚟一年，就算呢排無得密密見<br />\n希望你健健康康唔好病<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />留翻遲下日日糖癡豆<br />\n利申: I love u<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8428b4fd42e190260d5d1609d93475a11050c3a2","tid":2122172,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4828f1169f4cfebfb995593fb162963d306d053","tid":2122172,"uid":183576,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T00:22:28.000Z","msg":"因為佢係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T21:47:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"544f28607afe5ffd3e472b5449f3482eedd82c3d","tid":2122172,"uid":207328,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T21:59:12.000Z","msg":"識隱形 出世到而家都未搵到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9debdcec3e14e9392a19bf192db1110e628ce1","tid":2122172,"uid":286082,"like